query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.view_count >= 0 AND q.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('ant',
'apk',
'bar-chart',
'byte',
'each',
'installation',
'jasmine',
'lodash',
'navigation-drawer',
'node-modules',
'openmp',
'pthreads',
'xslt-1.0');
